Caer Corwell is the traditional seat of the heir to the throne of the Moonshaes High Kings; Prince Bryon Kendrick of Corwell is the High Queen's eldest son and dwells here from the spring to the autumn each year. The famous prince Tristan dwelt here during the Darkwalker wars, before himself ascending the throne and taking up residence as High King at Caer Calidyrr, many years ago...
